      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "此时本地一共有 3 个提交\n第一次提交中的 message 是 feat: 111\n现在需要将其修改为 feat: add 111",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "此时本地一共有 3 个提交\n第一次提交中的 message 是 feat: 111\n现在需要将其修改为 feat: add 111",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "xNQUPBuWMdr_qmI8WWODO",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -376.11090123763097,
      "y": -648.2777104016932,
      "width": 435.3998718261719,
      "height": 70,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "cross-hatch",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a5",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2048258223,
      "version": 555,
      "versionNonce": 609590731,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775107753820,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "输入命令 git rebase -i HEAD~3\n进行交互式变基",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "输入命令 git rebase -i HEAD~3\n进行交互式变基",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "wp5vg5VBfOnWpM9ISHBQq",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -374.9998070807287,
      "y": -349.94457942122244,
      "width": 540.3998413085938,
      "height": 630,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "cross-hatch",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a6",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 311558863,
      "version": 1360,
      "versionNonce": 1653698853,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775108671219,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "此时会进入到编辑模式\n如果配置了 core.editor \"code --wait\"\n会在我们执行 git rebase -i HEAD~3\n命令之后，会唤起 VSCode 并打开 .git/\nreebase-merge/git-rebase-todo 文件\n，在该文件的头部会显示当前的提交列表\n信息。\n\n此时我们可以修改第一行的提交消息为：\nr 1d83b16 feat: 111\n然后保存并关闭该文件\n\n随后，Git 会依次打开编辑器让你修改\n对应提交的消息\n此时将：feat: 111\n改为：feat: add 111\n保存之后并完毕，至此就完成了历史提交\n消息的重写工作",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "此时会进入到编辑模式\n如果配置了 core.editor \"code --wait\"\n会在我们执行 git rebase -i HEAD~3\n命令之后，会唤起 VSCode 并打开 .git/\nreebase-merge/git-rebase-todo 文件\n，在该文件的头部会显示当前的提交列表\n信息。\n\n此时我们可以修改第一行的提交消息为：\nr 1d83b16 feat: 111\n然后保存并关闭该文件\n\n随后，Git 会依次打开编辑器让你修改\n对应提交的消息\n此时将：feat: 111\n改为：feat: add 111\n保存之后并完毕，至此就完成了历史提交\n消息的重写工作",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "BCCVJKspzyJGOFNAJAM5b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -376.11090123762733,
      "y": 1047.833333637369,
      "width": 508.1997985839844,
      "height": 210,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
