      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": ".git/rebase-merge/git-rebase-todo\n文件完成编辑之后保存并关闭\n此时 git rebase -i HEAD~3 命令支持\n完毕会打印变基结果\n看到 successfully rebased 就意味着\n变基操作成功了",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": ".git/rebase-merge/git-rebase-todo\n文件完成编辑之后保存并关闭\n此时 git rebase -i HEAD~3 命令支持\n完毕会打印变基结果\n看到 successfully rebased 就意味着\n变基操作成功了",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "bly7qwsSK98t9DVbxsMFg",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -376.11090123763097,
      "y": 1630.0557246569006,
      "width": 501.19989013671875,
      "height": 210,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
